{"tid":1745345,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西灣河被槍傷男子被控非法集結　警方不排除加控罪行","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:32:16.000Z","uid":104865,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d12a140031db93bf6fbcc37c4951ded423f392","tid":1745345,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"本月11日在西灣河被交通警員以實彈槍傷的21歲男子，在出院後被警方拘捕和控告非法集結罪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被問到警方檢控的罪名為何與事發當日解釋的搶槍和襲警不同，以及是否仍堅持警員當初開槍的做法恰當，警務處處長鄧炳強未有回應開槍的決定是否恰當</span>，他表示，暫時用涉嫌非法集結拘捕有關人士，但不排除調查後會加控其他罪行，強調拘捕一刻撿控的罪名，不代表只是觸犯有關法例，經過調查後，有可能會以其他罪名檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493858-20191122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493858-20191122.htm&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylvCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=8fba33ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493858-20191122.htm&h=77d3fbf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493858-20191122.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殺完人 殺唔死 就出院拉佢番去打<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法救呢位手足"},{"pid":"0a61374a9c69c74901c39f4624f2dd24d3f8590d","tid":1745345,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"受左咁重傷 岩岩先出院 又拉入去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c331e20add1f1a66e7c93f5516094e6e1588714e","tid":1745345,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"推, 到時官一定問"},{"pid":"a3bd96c3f531e3feb3224fcca498e5b122eed9bc","tid":1745345,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"非法集結所以開槍？"},{"pid":"bd3784e09aa1797e0bd53424c9fb384df7fa0afb","tid":1745345,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:27:5